: Rt 20 at 0.6 km SE border with San Juan, 1610’, Mar 16, 2015 (RAJC) (
<emphasis id="2DC0EA82FFB5FFE4676E16C2D38627C3" bold="true" box="[557,690,439,464]" pageId="92" pageNumber="93">
<figureCitation id="878F2A15FFB5FFE4676E16C2D3AB27C3" box="[557,671,439,464]" captionStart="FIGURE 42" captionStartId="85.[151,249,1978,2000]" captionTargetBox="[405,1173,193,1956]" captionTargetId="figure@85.[405,1181,193,1956]" captionTargetPageId="85" captionText="FIGURE 42. Geographic distribution of: (A) Pogonomyrmex laticeps Santschi, (B) Pogonomyrmex mendozanus Cuezzo &amp; Claver, and (C) Pogonomyrmex tinogasta Johnson. The larger black circle in each panel denotes the type locality." pageId="92" pageNumber="93">Figure 42</figureCitation>
